were telling me about why you came here in the first 
place. How did you get to College Station for that

20:25.105 --> 20:28.849
first visit? Darius Mosher. Darius Mosher's 
parents lived in Stephenville. I had never heard

20:33.914 --> 20:37.057
of Texas A&M until I was in high school. You know, 
I'd heard of it, but I didn't think about it. But I

20:39.939 --> 20:44.003
loved Darius Mosher like a big brother to me, and 
I'd never seen a big football game. I had gone to

20:44.083 --> 20:47.967
Fort Worth to see Sammy Ball, some old people play. 
